OL,3,CWhat is Captagon, the highly-addictive
OL,4,Cdrug manufactured in Syria?
OL,6,FJust days after the fall of Syrian
OL,7,Fleader Bashar al-Assad, rebel fighters
OL,8,Fwho have taken hold of Syria's capital
OL,9,FDamascus, have uncovered huge
OL,10,Fstockpiles of Captagon, an illegal
OL,11,Famphetamine that's long been mass-
OL,12,Fproduced in the country.
OL,14,FVideo have been shared on social media
OL,15,Fof Syrian factories containing secret
OL,16,Fstashes of the drug.
OL,18,FWhat do we know about the substance
OL,19,Fthat is believed to have kept Assad in
OL,20,Fpower for so long?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
