OL,3,CWhat is Captagon, the highly-addictive
OL,4,Cdrug manufactured in Syria?
OL,6,FCaptagon is an illicit drug that is
OL,7,Fcheap to make and of which vast
OL,8,Fquantities can be produced in a
OL,9,Frelatively short period of time. It
OL,10,Facts a bit like a stimulant, making
OL,11,Fthe messages between your body and
OL,12,Fyour brain move faster.
OL,14,FBashar al-Assad was accused of turning
OL,15,FSyria into the world's leading
OL,16,Fmanufacturer of Captagon, with his
OL,17,Ffamily believed to have made billions
OL,18,Fshipping the drug all over the world.
