OL,3,CWhat is Captagon, the highly-addictive
OL,4,Cdrug manufactured in Syria?
OL,6,FIt is believed to be popular in parts
OL,7,Fof the Middle East, but shipments have
OL,8,Fbeen smuggled into Europe and to the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FThere have been several high-profile
OL,12,Fattempts to crackdown on the
OL,13,Fmanufacturing of Captagon. Videos
OL,14,Fposted online also show piles of the
OL,15,Fdrug being burned by groups once the
OL,16,Fpackages reach their destination.
OL,18,FIt appears to have had little effect
OL,19,Fon the production.
