OL,3,CWhat is Captagon, the highly-addictive
OL,4,Cdrug manufactured in Syria?
OL,6,FThe amphetamine is often hidden inside
OL,7,Fvegetable crates and electrical goods
OL,8,Ffor export. Some experts, including
OL,9,Fthose at the Observatory of Political
OL,10,Fand Economic Networks, suggest almost
OL,11,F#10 billion year was generated for
OL,12,FSyria through its sale. Two billion is
OL,13,Fthought to have gone directly to Assad
OL,14,Fand his family.
