OL,3,CWhat is Captagon, the highly-addictive
OL,4,Cdrug manufactured in Syria?
OL,6,FExperts who study the drug say they
OL,7,Ffear that people are not aware of the
OL,8,Frisks the drug carries, as it is not
OL,9,Fas well known as drugs like cocaine
OL,10,Fand ecstasy. It is also thought to be
OL,11,Fpopular in many Muslim countries where
OL,12,Fthe drug is often seen as an
OL,13,Falternative to alcohol.
OL,15,FThis latest stash found by opposition
OL,16,Fgroup Hayat Tahrir al Sham, also known
OL,17,Fas HTS, has been burned and destroyed.
OL,19,FA new government still needs to be
OL,20,Fformed in Syria after Assad was ousted.
